<title>Biographies</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<img src="discussi.gif">
<hr>
<center><h2>Biographies of Participants</h2></center>
<font face="arial" size=+1>
<ul>
<li><a href="bradbio.html">Senator Bill Bradley</a>
