http://www.atr.org:80/heritage/p_review/jul96/miller.html 204.71.237.87 19970210052712 text/html 19862
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 05:27:55 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 26-Jul-96 18:24:31 GMT
Content-length: 19678
Content-type: text/html
