<DOCOLDNO>IA037-000722-B043-102</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/heritage/library/categories/healthwel/fyi62.html 204.71.237.87 19970210052822 text/html 21923
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 05:29:00 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 29-May-96 14:03:43 GMT
