<HEAD>
<TITLE>Average cost of a loaf of bread: $1</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<P>
<CENTER><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/beeroped.html">next</a> | 7 of 8 | <a href="/atr/tax-presentation/boozoped.html">previous</a><br><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/paybread.html"><FONT SIZE=6>Average cost of a loaf of bread: $1.14</a>
<BR>
<BR>
<img src="/atr/sept96/bread.gif">
</FONT></B></U></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><U><FONT SIZE=4>Taxes Imposed on Bread Production and
Sales<BR>
