<P><TT><B><A NAME="31">31</A></B></TT> 5 U.S.C. 8348 permits the Secretary 
of the Treasury to exceed the debt limit for a temporary period in order to
manage the  Civil Service Retirement and Disability Trust  Fund. The &quot;disinvestment&quot;
procedure, in effect,  extinguishes Treasury bonds previously issued and held in
the trust fund by the Treasury.
</P>
