<center>
<h2>Issues '96: The Candidate's Briefing Book</h2>
<b><A HREF="/heritage">The Heritage Foundation</a></b>
</center><p>
<h3>Chapter 9 footnotes</h3>
<P>
<b><a href="chpt9.html">Return to Chapter 9</a></b>

<P><A NAME="1">1</A>     Charles J. Murray, &quot;What's Really Behind  the
SATScore Decline?&quot;  <CITE><U>The Public  Interest</U></CITE>, No. 106
(Winter 1992).
</P>
<P><A NAME="2">2</A>     Jeanne Allen and Michael J.  McLaughlin, &quot;A
Businessman's Guide to the Education  Reform Debate,&quot; Heritage Foundation 
<CITE><U>Backgrounder</U></CITE> No. 801, December 21, 1990, p. 4; data from 
