<p><li>4.2% of the native born population
<p><li>4.9% of all non-refugee immigrants admitted before 1980
<p><li>15.6% of all refugees admitted 1980-90 
</ul><p><b>Elderly over age 65 on Welfare (1990 Census)</b><ul>
